org.osgeo.mapguide

Class MgGeometricPathInstructionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgGeometricPathInstructionType

  • public class MgGeometricPathInstructionType
extends java.lang.Object
    MgGeometricPathInstructionType defines enumerated values used to specify the instructions contained in a geometric path. See MgGeometricPathIterator for a definition of a geometric path.
